1
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,520
Liao Fei, I told you.

2
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:20,520
I will give Xiao Fan an explanation.

3
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:22,560
But why did you touch Xiao Fang?

4
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:24,160
You touched Xiao Fang, didn't you?

5
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:25,280
Tell me first.

6
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:27,320
How exactly did Xiao Fan die?

7
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:47,600
At that time,

8
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,039
we were stealing ore.

9
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:57,360
Qiangzi and I saw someone at the door.

10
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,690
So we chased after them.

11
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,700
We didn't expect it to be Xiao Fan.

12
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,440
He was too impulsive then.

13
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,380
He wasn't thinking straight.

14
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:07,010
Before we could talk to him,

15
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:09,259
we chased him to the edge of the cliff.

16
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,900
An accident happened.

17
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,329
I admit it, Liao Fei.

18
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,920
If we hadn't chased him,

19
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,560
he wouldn't have run.

20
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,320
If he hadn't run,

21
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,960
Xiao Fan wouldn't have died.

22
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,640
Fei.

23
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:37,000
Gang has always been one of us.

24
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,970
He often helps the poor in our village.

25
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,960
And he's taken care of me since I was little.

26
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,880
I know him.

27
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,780
He wouldn't kill Xiao Fan.

28
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:47,280
Fei.

29
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,720
I came to you twice before.

30
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,760
Why didn't you tell me?

31
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:59,320
I had my reasons, Liao Fei.

32
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,240
Yang Gang, you have to admit,

33
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,600
you can't escape responsibility for Xiao Fan's death.

34
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,800
Shouldn't you give him an explanation?

35
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,780
Can I light some incense for Xiao Fan?

36
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,160
Xiao Fan.

37
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,320
I let you down.

38
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,200
Liao Fei.

39
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,060
Tell me, what else do you want?

40
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,680
Do you want a leg,

41
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,040
or an arm?

42
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:12,880
It's up to you.

43
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:14,840
Yang Gang.

44
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,480
Let me tell you.

45
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,880
I've always trusted you.

46
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:22,840
I never suspected you killed Xiao Fan.

47
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,200
I just wanted you to tell me the truth.

48
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:33,200
But you kept lying to me.

49
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,840
I'm sorry.

50
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,440
I know about Xiao Fang.

51
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,680
I didn't do it.

52
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:18,420
Mr. Gao, that kid from Dayang Village is here again.

53
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:20,840
He says he has something important for you.

54
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,400
Let him in.

55
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,120
Okay.

56
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:25,920
Come in.

57
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:35,690
The young man from Dayang Village.

58
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:43,760
Yang Gang.

59
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,170
You are persistent.

60
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,560
What is this?

61
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,850
Xiao Tianman's ledger.

62
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:11,880
It clearly lists all the bribery amounts,

63
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:17,480
the people, and the locations.

64
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,560
How did you get it?

65
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,320
This isn't fake, is it?

66
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:29,420
Why don't you check it yourself, Mr. Gao?

67
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:31,040
Whether it's usable,

68
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,040
how to use it,

69
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:33,480
and if it works,

70
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,120
is all up to you.

71
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,360
Yang Gang.

72
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,210
How much do you want?

73
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,800
Take my gold.

74
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,240
Just take your gold?

75
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,840
Just take my gold.

76
00:06:58,760 --> 00:06:59,560
Yang Gang.

77
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:04,400
I feel like there's a catch to your request.

78
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,600
Mr. Gao.

79
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,560
To be honest,

80
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:13,020
I really just need money for my mother's treatment.

81
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:15,380
I'll make this one deal and leave.

82
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,960
You have honor.

83
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:37,920
I'll take all your gold from now on.

84
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:41,960
Take this!

85
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,159
Brothers.

86
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,440
Sit down, you two.

87
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,850
Have a drink with me.

88
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,480
Sit.

89
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:11,800
Did Gao Shan turn us down again?

90
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:16,130
Tomorrow is the deadline to pay back the debt.

91
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,980
The interest is going to snowball again.

92
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,840
I might as well just die.

93
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,240
Come on.

94
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:26,410
Let's have a toast. Come on.

95
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,580
Look at all this money.

96
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,640
We won't have to suffer anymore.

97
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,080
Really.

98
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,920
You won't suffer anymore.

99
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,120
So much money.

100
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:16,920
Brother, when can I be discharged?

101
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:21,160
As long as you cooperate with the treatment,

102
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:23,160
you'll be discharged soon.

103
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:26,400
Brother, I really want to go back to school.

104
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:29,560
I'm falling far behind in my studies.

105
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:30,920
Didn't I just tell you?

106
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,880
Just cooperate with the treatment,

107
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,320
and you'll be discharged soon.

108
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,980
Then you can go back to school.

109
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:37,960
After I'm discharged,

110
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:40,000
we really have to thank Mr. Xiao.

111
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:42,520
He often sends people to check on me,

112
00:10:42,520 --> 00:10:44,280
and brings me so much food.

113
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:46,400
With my serious illness,

114
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:49,400
he's helped us so much.

115
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:51,240
We really must thank him.

116
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:55,080
Yes, we must.

117
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,400
Here.
